originalText.text:
Dr Saint Jean is truly heaven sent and literally is the best thing to happen to the Kingston area!!!
This was my 3rd and finally pregnancy and it was the best having Dr Saint Jean as my doctor. She was there every step of the way any questions or concerns I had she made she they were all answered. During my delivery being I had a scheduled C-section she was there making sure I was completely comfortable the whole entire time! I mean while I received my spinal she was the one holding me not the nurse! Yes she is the best!!!!.Once she started the C-section my baby was out in less than 20mins I also had my tubes tided i was completely done in the Operating room in less then 30mins seriously. My recovery was great and she made sure I had everything I needed. The ladies in the office also the best they literally made me feel like family every time I went in. Overall it was a great experience I highly recommend her she is the best in the area hands down.

originalText.text: I had a miscarriage and Dr. Saint Jean almost killed me. I was hemorrhaging and she didn't know how to get the medication I needed. After bleeding for 28 days I was told to go to another hospital. I'm so glad she at least did this as I met doctors who knew what they were doing. Needless to say the new doctors got the medication I needed with no problems and I was no longer hemorrhaging after 4 days under their care. Be very weary she doesn't know what she's doing.

originalText.text: She delivered my son Jacob 3 years ago who was wrapped around in his unbilical cord , she said " he was a miracle baby" I loved her she is a great doctor and god gave her an amazing gift may he keep giving her lots of health & blessings.  :)

originalText.text: Highly recommend.  She listened to my concerns and was calm during a very hectic time (COVID!) This was my second pregnancy but I feel like I learned a lot, understood the whole birthing process better and was treated with compassion throughout my entire pregnancy and especially during my post partum care.  WMC is a small practice which was very appealing to me.
